Don’t hurt your baby.

286
00:15:49,060 --> 00:15:50,620
I don’t know why.

287
00:15:52,940 --> 00:15:54,140
I just feel

288
00:15:55,780 --> 00:15:57,100
so scared today.

289
00:16:00,460 --> 00:16:01,180
Aunt,

290
00:16:03,780 --> 00:16:06,460
in the past, I always felt

291
00:16:07,020 --> 00:16:08,140
everything would be just fine

292
00:16:08,460 --> 00:16:10,060
