293
00:16:11,140 --> 00:16:12,180
But today,

294
00:16:14,860 --> 00:16:16,740
I was scared of him.

295
00:16:18,380 --> 00:16:20,140
His Majesty evicted Styling Director Li,

296
00:16:20,340 --> 00:16:21,660
