302
00:16:32,700 --> 00:16:33,980
There, there, stop crying.

303
00:16:34,460 --> 00:16:35,580
I hate her too.

304
00:16:38,020 --> 00:16:39,580
His Majesty is always magnanimous,

305
00:16:39,740 --> 00:16:41,100
but suddenly he made such a harsh move,

306
00:16:41,100 --> 00:16:42,380
which would surely terrify us.

307
00:16:43,100 --> 00:16:44,180
But think about it,

308
00:16:44,820 --> 00:16:46,460
if His Majesty was kind to

309
