312
00:16:50,100 --> 00:16:51,740
How can he rule the state?

313
00:16:53,580 --> 00:16:54,420
But…

314
00:16:55,940 --> 00:16:58,060
He’s only being nice to you

315
00:16:58,580 --> 00:17:02,460
