316
00:17:04,980 --> 00:17:05,860
Really?

317
00:17:09,580 --> 00:17:10,620
You silly girl.

318
00:17:12,380 --> 00:17:13,940
You are too straightforward.

319
00:17:15,180 --> 00:17:17,700
Today you recommended Xu Jingnu

320
00:17:18,620 --> 00:17:21,820
