325
00:17:32,260 --> 00:17:33,700
It’s all Li’s fault,

326
00:17:34,180 --> 00:17:35,300
leaving such an important

327
00:17:35,300 --> 00:17:36,460
vacancy all of a sudden,

328
00:17:36,940 --> 00:17:38,180
in charge of things

329
00:17:38,180 --> 00:17:39,220
every lady needs,

330
00:17:39,220 --> 00:17:40,060
and combing for

331
00:17:40,060 --> 00:17:41,180
His Majesty.

332
00:17:41,860 --> 00:17:42,740
I thought

333
00:17:42,980 --> 00:17:44,980
you told me to have more people on my side,

334
00:17:44,980 --> 00:17:45,540
so I…

335
00:17:47,540 --> 00:17:49,460
Besides, I was worried

336
00:17:49,460 --> 00:17:50,660
Miao’s people would take this position.

337
00:17:51,940 --> 00:17:52,540
You see,

338
00:17:52,860 --> 00:17:54,500
