342
00:18:01,980 --> 00:18:03,660
making me look so impatient.

343
00:18:05,220 --> 00:18:06,780
It’s okay.

344
00:18:07,780 --> 00:18:09,180
His Majesty said

345
00:18:09,500 --> 00:18:10,460
at the seventh night of July,

346
00:18:10,820 --> 00:18:12,180
each recommended maid

347
00:18:12,180 --> 00:18:13,180
