348
00:18:13,580 --> 00:18:15,500
and the one who makes the best hairstyle

349
00:18:15,700 --> 00:18:17,740
shall replace Styling Director Li.

350
00:18:18,860 --> 00:18:20,940
Xu is

351
00:18:21,180 --> 00:18:22,820
indeed very skillful.

352
00:18:23,740 --> 00:18:25,260
And your face

353
00:18:25,420 --> 00:18:26,940
makes the hairstyle

354
00:18:27,300 --> 00:18:29,220
unbeatable.

355
00:18:30,020 --> 00:18:30,820
Look,

356
00:18:31,620 --> 00:18:33,140
ever since you started to dance,

357
00:18:33,260 --> 00:18:35,500
till you become His Majesty’s woman,

358
00:18:35,980 --> 00:18:37,460
no one could be more attractive

359
00:18:37,460 --> 00:18:38,820
