but

365
00:18:49,620 --> 00:18:51,180
he has already given you

366
00:18:52,220 --> 00:18:53,900
all the advantages.

367
00:18:58,620 --> 00:18:59,340
Your Highness,

368
00:19:00,100 --> 00:19:01,820
I know you didn’t want me

369
00:19:02,660 --> 00:19:04,340
to compete against Madam Zhang today,

370
00:19:05,940 --> 00:19:07,260
but you

371
00:19:07,620 --> 00:19:09,020
saved me

372
00:19:09,220 --> 00:19:10,300
from the embarrassment.

373
00:19:11,780 --> 00:19:12,860
You are

374
00:19:13,620 --> 00:19:14,820
never a competitive person,

375
00:19:15,300 --> 00:19:16,380
and you are not good at it either.

376
00:19:17,900 --> 00:19:19,180
Why did you do that today?

377
00:19:20,940 --> 00:19:22,260
She’s so arrogant, domineering,

378
00:19:23,700 --> 00:19:26,220
overbearing, and looks down upon me.

379
00:19:26,780 --> 00:19:29,860
I can bear with her, and I don’t envy her.

380
00:19:30,980 --> 00:19:32,060
But she just believes

381
00:19:32,060 --> 00:19:34,540
