386
00:19:44,500 --> 00:19:45,860
I have no choice.

387
00:19:47,060 --> 00:19:48,100
So what?

388
00:19:49,340 --> 00:19:52,380
You’ll compete against her from now on?

389
00:20:01,100 --> 00:20:01,900
Your Highness.

390
00:20:02,660 --> 00:20:03,420
At least today

391
00:20:03,420 --> 00:20:04,820
I can’t let her

392
00:20:04,820 --> 00:20:06,180
put her spy around His Majesty,

393
00:20:07,260 --> 00:20:09,180
who can slander Huirou at any time.

394
00:20:10,340 --> 00:20:11,420
You know

395
00:20:12,940 --> 00:20:14,620
I just want to

396
00:20:15,580 --> 00:20:17,700
be with you

397
00:20:18,820 --> 00:20:20,460
and His Majesty,

398
00:20:21,900 --> 00:20:23,060
raise Huirou

399
00:20:23,940 --> 00:20:25,820
and Zuixinglai.

400
00:20:27,500 --> 00:20:29,540
I hope Huirou can be married to a good family,

401
00:20:30,940 --> 00:20:33,060
and Zuixinglai can have a promising future.

402
00:20:35,740 --> 00:20:37,340
As for His Majesty love,

403
00:20:40,020 --> 00:20:41,540
I do want it,

404
00:20:43,540 --> 00:20:44,660
but I am not greedy for it.

405
00:20:46,220 --> 00:20:47,140
I can live without it.

406
00:20:49,540 --> 00:20:50,980
But I’m Huirou’s mother,

407
00:20:53,220 --> 00:20:54,780
I must do everything I can

408
00:20:55,060 --> 00:20:56,260
to protect my daughter.

409
00:21:04,740 --> 00:21:05,460
Get up.

410
00:21:12,420 --> 00:21:13,260
Xinhe,

411
00:21:15,500 --> 00:21:16,460
do you think

412
00:21:17,540 --> 00:21:19,580
His Majesty would suspect Huirou
and stop loving her

413
00:21:20,100 --> 00:21:23,180
just because someone said something?

414
00:21:24,620 --> 00:21:26,300
Even if he’s surrounded by people

415
00:21:26,420 --> 00:21:28,660
who slander Huirou,

416
00:21:29,140 --> 00:21:30,660
will he allow others

417
00:21:30,740 --> 00:21:32,340
to do harm to his own girl?

418
00:21:39,100 --> 00:21:39,820
Your Highness,

419
00:21:41,980 --> 00:21:43,220
with all due respect,

420
00:21:44,460 --> 00:21:46,860
Xinhe has to say something.

421
00:21:49,500 --> 00:21:50,700
I can’t tell

422
00:21:50,700 --> 00:21:51,900
some thorough reasoning,

423
00:21:54,020 --> 00:21:55,460
but I can’t understand

424
00:21:57,220 --> 00:21:57,900
if His Majesty...

425
00:22:01,100 --> 00:22:03,460
His Majesty has a sober mind,

426
00:22:04,540 --> 00:22:06,020
why would he pamper Madam Zhang only

427
00:22:07,020 --> 00:22:08,660
with a wife like Your Highness?

428
00:22:15,540 --> 00:22:16,300
Huaiji,

429
00:22:17,740 --> 00:22:18,660
you’ve been listening to

430
00:22:18,660 --> 00:22:19,620
officials’ proposals

431
00:22:19,620 --> 00:22:20,700
for some time.

432
00:22:21,260 --> 00:22:22,620
Especially the advice

433
00:22:22,620 --> 00:22:23,580
from imperial censors.

434
00:22:24,580 --> 00:22:25,420
Let me ask you,

435
00:22:26,020 --> 00:22:27,340
do you think their advice

436
00:22:27,540 --> 00:22:28,500
is correct?

437
00:22:29,340 --> 00:22:31,340
Or how much do you think

438
00:22:31,380 --> 00:22:32,460
is correct?

439
00:22:34,460 --> 00:22:36,060
Tell me what you think.

440
00:22:37,780 --> 00:22:40,660
I, I don’t understand the politics.

441
00:22:41,100 --> 00:22:42,900
But sometimes when the officials

442
00:22:42,900 --> 00:22:44,580
are talking about local affairs,

443
00:22:46,260 --> 00:22:48,780
like people’s conventions,

444
00:22:49,380 --> 00:22:51,180
like sellers and shops,

445
00:22:51,860 --> 00:22:52,940
I think

446
00:22:53,140 --> 00:22:55,580
they are sometimes taking things for granted.

447
00:22:56,940 --> 00:22:58,900
And today,

448
00:22:59,860 --> 00:23:01,660
most of the things they said about the harem

449
00:23:02,380 --> 00:23:04,780
are incorrect.

450
00:23:05,300 --> 00:23:08,620
They are just some wild assumptions out there.

451
00:23:09,860 --> 00:23:12,020
Officials are loyal

452
00:23:12,940 --> 00:23:14,020
and worried about the state,

453
00:23:14,060 --> 00:23:15,740
they can devote all their heart
and life to the court.

454
00:23:16,460 --> 00:23:17,260
But

455
00:23:17,540 --> 00:23:19,500
they assume others as the evilest

456
00:23:20,100 --> 00:23:21,420
or the stupidest.

457
00:23:28,980 --> 00:23:31,300
In a hundred proposals from the imperial censors,

458
00:23:31,980 --> 00:23:33,220
only two or three

459
00:23:33,780 --> 00:23:36,900
are unbiased, pointing out problems,

460
00:23:37,060 --> 00:23:39,220
and giving useful ideas, suggestions

461
00:23:39,220 --> 00:23:40,260
and feasible plans.

462
00:23:41,220 --> 00:23:42,060
But,

463
00:23:43,700 --> 00:23:46,020
but when implementing those plans,

464
00:23:47,460 --> 00:23:49,660
there are always countless unexpected problems.

465
00:23:51,540 --> 00:23:52,620
Two or three proposals?

466
00:23:54,260 --> 00:23:55,020
Among the rest, about 30

467
00:23:56,100 --> 00:23:57,340
of them

468
00:23:57,380 --> 00:23:58,820
are just shuffling through the routine,

469
00:23:58,820 --> 00:24:00,460
full of worthless gibberish.

470
00:24:00,780 --> 00:24:01,620
30 of them

471
00:24:01,780 --> 00:24:03,980
are empty talks,

472
00:24:04,940 --> 00:24:08,340
and 20 of them are full of worries
about the state and people,

473
00:24:09,260 --> 00:24:11,220
but with limited horizon

474
00:24:11,660 --> 00:24:12,580
and

475
00:24:12,660 --> 00:24:14,420
biased view.

476
00:24:15,380 --> 00:24:16,340
16 or 17 of them

477
00:24:17,060 --> 00:24:18,980
are solid impeachment,

478
00:24:19,580 --> 00:24:21,740
but their solution is

479
00:24:22,180 --> 00:24:24,340
unrealistic empty talk,

480
00:24:25,140 --> 00:24:26,020
or

481
00:24:27,980 --> 00:24:30,100
are used for other issues.

482
00:24:33,260 --> 00:24:34,620
Take today’s discussion as an example.

483
00:24:35,420 --> 00:24:37,620
They said the disasters

484
00:24:38,180 --> 00:24:40,260
were caused by having too many
useless women in the harem.

485
00:24:44,260 --> 00:24:46,580
Whose words are closer to the truth?

486
00:24:47,700 --> 00:24:48,780
Is it because of the women

487
00:24:49,500 --> 00:24:51,580
in the harem like they said,

488
00:24:52,420 --> 00:24:54,140
or because officials outside

489
00:24:54,540 --> 00:24:55,740
who have a dissolute life

490
00:24:56,660 --> 00:24:58,900
as what the combing stewardess said?

491
00:25:00,620 --> 00:25:01,380
But

492
00:25:01,940 --> 00:25:04,060
I evicted the combing stewardess,

493
00:25:04,180 --> 00:25:06,620
not because what they said

494
00:25:06,620 --> 00:25:07,580
is correct,

495
