but because everything

496
00:25:10,540 --> 00:25:11,860
has rules.

497
00:25:12,740 --> 00:25:15,660
All the officials,
no matter at the court or in the harem

498
00:25:15,860 --> 00:25:18,260
have their dos and don’ts.

499
00:25:19,540 --> 00:25:22,500
The imperial censors did what they should do,

500
00:25:23,380 --> 00:25:24,860
As for its correctness

501
00:25:25,340 --> 00:25:26,780
and feasibility,

502
00:25:27,260 --> 00:25:28,660
that’s something ministries

503
00:25:28,660 --> 00:25:29,860
and I should think about.

504
00:25:31,180 --> 00:25:32,420
But the combing stewardess

505
00:25:33,060 --> 00:25:34,740
did something she shouldn’t do.

506
00:25:34,740 --> 00:25:35,700
She broke the rule,

507
00:25:37,260 --> 00:25:40,100
and even gave me reasons

508
00:25:40,580 --> 00:25:41,500
to seduce me

509
00:25:42,140 --> 00:25:44,140
from not being restrained by the officials
and the people.

510
00:25:46,620 --> 00:25:48,980
You want them to restrain you?

511
00:25:50,940 --> 00:25:54,660
No matter how smart and benevolent one is,

512
00:25:55,660 --> 00:25:57,140
if he has no restraint,

513
00:25:58,060 --> 00:25:59,340
he will eventually be obsessed with love,
be greedy for desire,

514
00:26:00,060 --> 00:26:02,980
and cut loose from rules and manners

515
00:26:03,260 --> 00:26:04,340
because of benevolence,

516
00:26:05,060 --> 00:26:06,740
feelings and desires.

517
00:26:08,820 --> 00:26:11,100
An ordinary person might only ruin himself
by doing so.

518
00:26:11,700 --> 00:26:13,020
But an emperor

519
00:26:14,860 --> 00:26:15,980
will ruin the whole state.

520
00:26:17,700 --> 00:26:18,420
But

521
00:26:18,780 --> 00:26:20,020
if what they said is incorrect,

522
00:26:20,780 --> 00:26:21,740
and most of it is useless,

523
00:26:22,260 --> 00:26:23,660
why does such restraint is needed?

524
00:26:27,580 --> 00:26:28,820
The imperial censors

525
00:26:29,260 --> 00:26:30,900
are supposed to restrain
the emperor and the officials.

526
00:26:31,220 --> 00:26:32,500
They can give advice

527
00:26:32,780 --> 00:26:33,940
on anything.

528
00:26:34,580 --> 00:26:35,580
Huaiji,

529
00:26:36,420 --> 00:26:38,220
do you think imperial censors

530
00:26:38,660 --> 00:26:39,420
can have more insightful remarks
on water conservancy

531
00:26:39,420 --> 00:26:41,100
than officials
who have been working on it for 30 years?

532
00:26:42,300 --> 00:26:43,460
Or they have more thorough understanding

533
00:26:44,300 --> 00:26:45,700
of the disadvantages of tax system

534
00:26:45,700 --> 00:26:47,180
than the ministries?

535
00:26:48,060 --> 00:26:48,980
Or they know better

536
00:26:52,700 --> 00:26:53,820
what an emperor should do

537
00:26:53,980 --> 00:26:56,140
to govern a country

538
00:26:56,220 --> 00:26:57,100
than me,

539
00:26:57,100 --> 00:26:59,380
who have been listening to the debates
since I was 8,

540
00:26:59,540 --> 00:27:01,900
and been

541
00:27:02,140 --> 00:27:03,540
on the throne for 30 years?

542
00:27:04,220 --> 00:27:06,740
No, they can’t,

543
00:27:08,140 --> 00:27:10,140
most of the times they can’t.

544
00:27:11,460 --> 00:27:12,900
Their existence is

545
00:27:13,580 --> 00:27:15,980
to let people who’s working on it

546
00:27:16,180 --> 00:27:17,900
be cautious,

547
00:27:18,380 --> 00:27:20,180
and prudent,

548
00:27:21,260 --> 00:27:22,700
so that they would always stay alert,

549
00:27:22,900 --> 00:27:24,940
and fulfill their duty.

550
00:27:25,460 --> 00:27:27,060
Even for the 2 or 3 unbiased impeachments

551
00:27:27,220 --> 00:27:28,980
out of 100,

552
00:27:29,260 --> 00:27:32,300
I must be cautious and conscientious,

553
00:27:32,740 --> 00:27:34,580
restrain all my feelings and desires,

554
00:27:35,500 --> 00:27:36,660
and be unbiased.

555
00:27:38,700 --> 00:27:42,700
I also need all the people to know

556
00:27:43,220 --> 00:27:44,940
the Court and I

557
00:27:45,420 --> 00:27:46,500
are always

558
00:27:47,420 --> 00:27:49,380
under their surveillance,

559
00:27:50,700 --> 00:27:51,860
so that they can feel assured.

560
00:27:59,660 --> 00:28:01,780
I’m so lucky to be in the palace

561
00:28:02,740 --> 00:28:07,340
and instructed by Your Majesty.

562
00:28:15,620 --> 00:28:16,300
Silly boy.

563
00:28:16,500 --> 00:28:17,220
Get up.

564
00:28:17,420 --> 00:28:19,180
Come here.

565
00:28:25,100 --> 00:28:28,020
I instruct you in person
out of some personal interest.

566
00:28:30,660 --> 00:28:32,420
You are extremely clever and innocent,

567
00:28:33,380 --> 00:28:36,900
I want you to be with Zuixinglai.

568
00:28:39,020 --> 00:28:42,300
Do you want me to

569
00:28:42,580 --> 00:28:44,060
serve the prince in the Pavilion of Phoenix?

570
00:28:47,020 --> 00:28:49,700
Yes and no.

571
00:28:50,900 --> 00:28:51,820
He doesn’t need

572
00:28:51,820 --> 00:28:53,340
another servant.

573
00:28:57,460 --> 00:29:00,020
All the intelligent officials at the court

574
00:29:00,300 --> 00:29:01,300
work for the state.

575
00:29:01,980 --> 00:29:05,020
But I want to give him a merciful

576
